bio: Competed in doubles at Australian Open in 1987-89 and Wimbledon in 1990...Reached Bordeaux, FRA doubles SF in 1987 w/Fricker (l. to Cahill/Woodforde)...Won Dijon, FRA Challenger doubles title in 1988 w/Endelman (d.
